Address Lifecycle
=================

This fixture checks literate statemachine parsing from a `.cml` document.
Prelude narrative before the structural section must be ignored.

# STATEMACHINE

Narrative text before the first state machine definition must not become a machine.

## SUMMARY

Short summary for the statemachine section.

## lifecycle
rule {
  state = [
    {
      name = Draft
      transition = [
        {
          guard = publish
          to = Published
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      name = Published
    }
  ]
}

## Overview
This section is narrative and must not be treated as a state machine definition.
